        Let's take a look at the outfit in this picture.
        See how it matches with the natural green and cream palette.
        The colour of this hat was chosen from this matching palette so that it would compliment this outfit and this is why it works so well.
        The skirt and shoes both have green and cream in them and the top is either cream or off-white.
