      %p
        It was clear to see that many people are choosing to wear hats of all types in the sun these days and there are more than enough styles to choose from.
        There were also a couple of visors being worn on the day, but I have not included them here.

      %p
        There was something else I noticed that day too: all the hats looked great and they all seemed to be working very well for the wearer.
        So the best thing you can do now is to go and start trying some hats on right away.
        See how they look, but more importantly, see how you feel wearing them.
        If you don’t feel right then move on and try another style.
        If you don’t find the right one then take your time.

      %p
        Pick the right style and the right colour for you and your wardrobe,
        you will feel so confident wearing it that you may find yourself wearing it all summer long and you will wonder why you ever went anywhere without it.
        The right one will almost speak to you when you find it and you will know it is yours.

